<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="eu-citizens-in-the-uk-your-stories">EU citizens in the UK: your stories</h2>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9E9ZMAJxza0&feature=youtu.be">People like me: Klara</a></p>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ov0rxseEiQo&feature=youtu.be">People like me: Francisco</a></p>

<h2 id="eu-citizens-in-the-uk-eu-settlement-scheme-overview">EU citizens in the UK: EU Settlement Scheme overview</h2>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://youtu.be/73M5zBNcTTA">Scheme overview</a></p>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X0Thl2nfZjo">How to use the â€˜EU Exit: ID Document Checkâ€™ app</a></p>

<p>The employer toolkit contains leaflets, factsheets and a briefing pack to help employers across the UK communicate clear and consistent messages about the EU Settlement Scheme.</p>

<p>EU citizens and their families can <a href="https://www.gov.uk/eu-settled-status">apply for settled status or pre-settled status under the EU Settlement Scheme</a>.</p>

<p>If the UK leaves the EU without a deal, youâ€™ll need to be living in the UK before it leaves the EU to apply to the EU Settlement Scheme. The deadline for applying will be 31 December 2020.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

